\cos\theta + \cos3\theta + ... + \cos((2n+1)\theta
\sin\theta + \sin3\theta + ... + \sin((2n+1)\theta
\theta \in
e^{i\theta}+e^{3i\theta}+\cdots +e^{(2n+1)i\theta}=e^{i\theta}\frac{1-e^{2(n+1)i\theta}}{1-e^{2i\theta}}=\frac{2 (e^{2(n+1)i\theta}-1)}{\sin\theta}
\sin\theta \neq 0
\operatorname{Re }(e^{i\theta}+e^{3i\theta}+\cdots +e^{(2n+1)i\theta}) = \cos\theta+\cos3\theta +\cdots + \cos(2n+1)\theta
\operatorname{Im }(e^{i\theta}+e^{3i\theta}+\cdots +e^{(2n+1)i\theta}) = \sin\theta+\sin3\theta +\cdots + \sin(2n+1)\theta
\cos\theta+\cos3\theta +\cdots + \cos(2n+1)\theta = \frac{2(\cos 2(n+1)\theta -1)}{\sin\theta}
\sin\theta+\sin3\theta +\cdots + \sin(2n+1)\theta = \frac{2\sin2(n+1)\theta}{\sin\theta}
\sin\theta\neq 0
